snippet.title: Amber Heard Won't Lose Role In Aquaman 2
snippet.description:
Amber Heard Won't Lose Role In Aquaman 2 
Subscribe To InformOverload: http://bit.ly/2xB5CqA

So far, close to 400 thousand people have signed a petition to urge Warner Brothers to remove Amber Heard from the cast of aquaman 2. There are also calls to remove her as the spokesperson for Loreal. But its unlikely Amber heard will lose either of those opportunities, I’m going to tell you why and you’re probably going to get really mad, right now on IO
